29/09/2006 - Added PROJECT.BASE parameter to XSL service catalogue generation. DJWright
13/12/2006 - Added Refdata zip.  DJWright
28/06/2007 - Added Batch zip.  CJHutt
27/02/2008 - Added build-reports-templates-only.  Chris Vincent
29/10/2009 - Chris Vincent: changed build.num.major to CCBC_ and bulid.num.minor to build.app.num
03/11/2009 - Chris Vincent: copy-and-zip-batch no longer called as part of build-deployment target
